title: [1508521049] Gordon Ramsay at Christmas - OUTTAKES
description:
So we shot some videos with the man himself - and it just goes to show, doing this job isn't as easy as Mr. Ramsay makes it look. We hope you enjoy this video and thanks for all your support.
